<h3 id="viewport-based-hiding">Viewport-based hiding</h3>
<p>Breakpoint tokens are also available in utility classes for hiding content based on the screen size. The class format is <code>.hide-below-[breakpoint]</code> or <code>.hide-above-[breakpoint]</code>. Example:</p>

